      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed by independent senior analyst at each participating organization. Modeling protocol document (MPD-001 rev C) specifies all boundary condition, contact, and loading definitions. Boundary conditions verified against physical fixture drawings. Gradation 2 achieved."
