      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties from certified material test reports for each lot; geometry from CMM-measured production parts; boundary conditions from ASTM F1717 fixture calibration records.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and Poisson's ratio sourced from certified material test reports for the Ti-6Al-4V rod and screw lots used in testing. Screw and rod geometry digitized via coordinate measuring machine (CMM) with ±0.005 mm accuracy. Fixture stiffness characterized experimentally and incorporated as elastic boundary conditions. Gradation 3 achieved."
