      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions, loading) match experimental test conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "One-to-one correspondence established between model inputs and experimentally characterized test parameters. Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of test specimens. Material inputs from lot-specific test reports. Loading and boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture as characterized by fixture compliance testing. Gradation 3 achieved."
