      "rationale": "The three QoIs selected (construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement) are the primary outputs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly reflect construct mechanical integrity relevant to clinical performance. Stiffness relates to load sharing; yield force and force at 40 mm bracket the failure envelope. Gradation 3 achieved."
