    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment for the non-cannulated pedicle screw FEA model is Accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (Gradation 2 achieved vs. Gradation 3 required) is mitigated by the conservative nature of ASTM F1717 loading and the strong quantitative agreement demonstrated across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96 for all). The model ensemble approach across three independent organizations further strengthens confidence. The package is submitted under the Minimal profile; project requirements governing this analysis are maintained in the design history file per the sponsor's quality management system.",
